{"tid":2401630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國又贏 CIA局長候選人曾收中美交流基金會捐款","createTime":"2021-02-10T01:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T01:27:45.000Z","uid":13745,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8fbae39ca2c02915f46401ac175ef931bf10a0b9","tid":2401630,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T01:22:57.000Z","msg":"卡內基國際和平基金會（Carnegie Endowment for International Peace）主席伯恩斯（William Burns）獲美國總統拜登提名，出任中情局局長。美國網媒《Daily Caller》翻查資料，發現基金會在伯恩斯任內，與中國關係密切，除了讓一名中國政協加入基金會理事會，也收取該政協和董建華成立的「中美交流基金會」超過100萬元（美元，下同）捐款，安排國會職員到北京交流，與中國共產黨員共晉午餐。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最緊要利用收集情報發大財賺人民幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210210/WTCOPKVLVZARTCSE2JQ4A5Z6R4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210210%2FWTCOPKVLVZARTCSE2JQ4A5Z6R4%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQlT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=1fdf860e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210210%2FWTCOPKVLVZARTCSE2JQ4A5Z6R4%2F&h=8ff7917e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210210/WTCOPKVLVZARTCSE2JQ4A5Z6R4/</a>"},{"pid":"3e18ecc907304ca53cb7229aece438d0e6e5f248","tid":2401630,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T01:24:19.000Z","msg":"特朗普出任美國總統期間，卡內基國際和平基金會經常為中國官媒環球電視網（CGTN）就外交政策作訪問。新任白宮國家安全顧問沙利文（Jake Sullivan）於2017年12月、任職基金會高級研究員時，也接受過CGTN訪問，批評特朗普的中東政策。"},{"pid":"8d5414dd12834a0e73d60fc5b325aa4638f56aef","tid":2401630,"uid":13745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T01:25:35.000Z","msg":"2019年，伯恩斯以基金會主席身份，去信邀請美國國會職員訪問北京，建立「有關中美關係的跨黨派對話」，最終11人於同年11月成行。<br />\n擺明係外國代理人咁都可以做中情局長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img